version_description: It fixes a lot of issues with a different tab.
This version is different in the fact that the chords are simpler - more suited to a beginner. Also, the right chords have been put in the right places and the instrumentals are correct.

song_name: Por El Poder De Tu Amor

version_description: None of the versions of this song I found are truly accurate. Some have unnecessary chords in them that make no sense and others simply have the wrong chords. I think my version is the most streamlined, accurate, and simple to play. I normally don't make tabs but I was frustrated at the versions available and decided to use theirs as a template. Some tabs have some things right, others have other things right. I decided to take what's accurate from the tabs available and make a tab that's easy and accurate.
